kModal_main_3615547\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qyp1665702633319.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qyp1665702633319.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qyp1665702633319.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qyp1665702633319\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Width of the border around the widget in pixels, if \n                                Frame is true. Default is <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> pixel.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__topic_d104075e1_d104076e1_d104077e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__p_d104078e1_d104079e1_d104080e1\">FrameWidth<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__section_w848ab1b5b3_w849ab1b5_w850ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__p_d104081e1_d104082e1_d104083e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"FrameWidth=3\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__section_w851ab1b5b5_w852ab1b5_w853ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__table_d12281e1_d12282e1_d12283e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__table_d12281e1_d12282e1_d12283e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__table_d12281e1_d12282e1_d12283e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qyp1665702633319__table_d12281e1_d12282e1_d12283e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qyp1665702633319__table_d12281e1_d12282e1_d12283e1__entry__2\">Positive integer indicating the border line\n                        width in pixels. Default is <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__section_dqm_fzn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1019512e117\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__table_d12284e1_d12285e1_d12286e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> must be\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n<p class=\"p\">For command buttons, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> must be\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>.</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__section_tmg_hzn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1019512e176\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__p_d104090e1_d104091e1_d104092e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__pre_yb1_3zn_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"frame=true<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>framewidth=4\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__section_zwh_3zn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1019512e198\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__ul_hjk_jzn_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__li_d41813e1_d41814e1_d41815e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qyp1665702633319__li_d41816e1_d41817e1_d41818e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svg1665702629592.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Frame</a><p>Determines whether a border is displayed around the widget at run time. True or False. The default value depends on the widget.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$properties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615547\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615547\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Frame Width (FrameWidth) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Width of the border around the widget in pixels, if Frame is true. Default is 1 pixel. FrameWidth = Number Example: \"FrameWidth=3\" Value Description Number Positive integer indicating the border line width in pixels. Default is 1 . Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Frame must be True For command buttons, Representation must be Uniface . Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics. $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"frame=true ; framewidth=4\" Copy Applies To CommandButton utabex (TabEx) Related Links Frame Determines whether a border is displayed around the widget at run time. True or False. The default value depends on the widget. $properties Return or set the current widget properties of a field. $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}